metadata.name: Lonely road.
metadata.description: This is it, you took the path no one else would, the unknown, you took passion over stability no one believes in it but you, no one can see it the way you do, family and friends think you are stupid but you roll with it. In your heart you know you can do it. but you can't stop dwelling on why you did it. Are you going to fail the mission or prove everyone wrong? when the end comes does the happiness come, or do we stay on the lonely road.
